public class TransmissionGearPosition
extends Measurement<State<TransmissionGearPosition.GearPosition>>
implements VehicleMeasurement

The TransmissionGearPosition is the actual current gear of the transmission. This measurement is the current actual gear, not the selected or desired gear by the driver or computer.
